  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Recovery of sea cards hoarded for smuggling to Sri Lanka",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "480 kg of sea cards, which were hoarded to be smuggled to Sri Lanka, were recovered near the Mandapam camp in Tamil Nadu yesterday (30) evening.",
        "Forest Department officials have received confidential information that sea cards are being stored near Mandapam from Vedalai beach area to be smuggled to Sri Lanka.",
        "Following this, the forest department rushed to the area and confiscated about 480 kg of sea card stored for smuggling to Sri Lanka and are conducting an investigation.",
        "According to the forest department, the seized sea card has an international value of Rs 50 lakh."
      ],
